00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:35,159
EnglishPod.com Like every other citizen, I wish the new president and all who will labor with him, Godspeed.

2
00:00:35,920 --> 00:00:40,240
I pray that the coming years will be blessed with peace and prosperity for all.

3
00:00:42,439 --> 00:00:52,340
Our people expect their president and the Congress to find essential agreement on questions of great importance, the wise resolution of which will better shape the future of our great nation.

4
00:00:53,339 --> 00:01:01,820
My own relations with Congress began on a remote and tenuous basis when, long ago, a member of the Senate appointed me to West Point.

5
00:01:02,979 --> 00:01:08,859
I then had the pleasure of building more intimate relationships with Congress during the war and the immediate post-war period.

6
00:01:10,099 --> 00:01:15,680
Finally, we have progressed to the mutually interdependent relationship we've had during these past eight years.

